## Extensions

Project-specific guidance and accumulated knowledge layer onto skills and agents at runtime:

- **Lessons** — `~/Claude/{project}/lessons/*.md`. Authored by `/learn` after retrospectives; loaded into every skill at startup via the runtime context loader.
- **Skill overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/skill_<name>.md`. Loaded into the matching skill at startup via the runtime context loader.
- **Agent overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/agent_booping-<name>.md`. Loaded into the matching agent at startup via the runtime context loader.

## Hard rules

- **`/help` never writes files.** If the user needs scaffolding, hand off to `/install`.

